REQUIREMENTS:




STEPS:
STEP1:
#step up web

1.launch web server in public subnet

update the packages

install web server

2.clone code 
git clone 

goto project repository

cd

copy the code to the target
cp -r /present path/* /usr/share/nginx/html

Update Nginx Configuration
sudo vi /etc/nginx/sites-available/default

server {
    listen 80;
    server_name your-domain-or-ip;

    root /usr/share/nginx/html;
    index index.html;

    location / {
        try_files $uri $uri/ =404;
    }
}

Restart Nginx
sudo systemctl restart nginx

check ports are enable or not
port 80
